idCitation.resTitle: Affordable, Moderate, Achievable Bonus Unit Incentive Area

dataIdInfo.idPurp: Residential bonus unit boundary delineating eligibility of parcels for receiving affordable, moderate, and achievable residential bonus units (in replacement of residential development rights).
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Residential bonus unit boundary delineating eligibility of parcels for receiving affordable, moderate, and achievable residential bonus units (in replacement of residential development rights). This boundary was updated in July 2021 to include areas that are within ½ mile of existing transit, ½ miles from Town Centers, and areas zoned for multi-family residential housing. Parcels may be partially within this boundary to receive a residential bonus unit.
